So in this trial, you find a very interesting pattern that engraftment of the donor microbiota

00:06:27.300 --> 00:06:35.820
seems to matter a lot. Patients in whom these donor microbiota engrafted well, those are in the

00:06:35.820 --> 00:06:42.100
bottom curve, had a much, much lower incidence of acute GVHD grade 2 to 4 compared to those who

00:06:42.100 --> 00:06:47.200
